==Le Cateau road junction==

==Soesterberg Airfield==
The air base at Soesterberg is being used by the Luftwaffe to launch air raids on Britain.
It's protected by fairly strong flak.

==Wesel road bridge==

==Berlin U-boat Works==
The submarine works in Berlin are responsible for a large part of German production of ocean-going U-boats.
They have moderately strong flak defences.

